name: trXde.fun
description: trXde.fun is the first memecoin binary option trading platform, that let you gain from guessing if the price of a given ticker is gonna be higher or lower in the next minute. The system works by first determining winning bets, calculating each user's share of the total pool, then processing actual blockchain payments automatically after each round So each pool will have a different payout both in sol amount and as payout multiplier let's say user 1 trade 0.1 on dump, user 2 trades 0.1 on pump, the payout will be 0.2 (minus fees) to the winner and the multiplier will be 2x
